    "scene": "bridge",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Rumors bounce wild—none of them blend,",
    "start": 130.25,
    "end": 134.63,
    "scene": "bridge",
    "big": false
  },
  {
    "text": "Dom Shady just wants the script to amend.",
    "start": 134.93,
    "end": 139.32,
    "scene": "bridge",
    "big": false
  },
  {
